Mirabito Rewards Plus savings card
  Rewards Plus is Mirabito’s exciting customer loyalty program that offers members great rewards and money-saving opportunities when they shop at Mirabito Convenience Stores and Mirabito Energy Products.
Sign-up is FREE and you can stay in-tune with upcoming specials and offers through our web site or by visiting any of our participating locations.  
How it works
  Pick up a free Mirabito Rewards Plus card by visiting any Mirabito Convenience Store location.
Rewards Plus cards can also be requested online or by calling 1-866-647-2248.
Begin earning cents off and getting great discounts immediately by showing your card.  
Additional Rewards for Mirabito Energy Products Customers
  Mirabito Energy Products customers can earn rewards from propane or fuel oil deliveries, any service or equipment installation, or purchase of pellets or coal.
Mirabito Energy Products customers can choose whether to redeem at the pump or for various Energy Products offerings. Customers choosing to redeem at the pump will earn 1¢ for every 10 gallons of fuel delivered. Customers choosing to not redeem at the pump can redeem Rewards by going to the online Rewards Portal or calling 1-866-647-2248. Current redemption offers include a certificate to put towards any home energy bill, percentage off of a Total Comfort Plan (TCP), or percentage off of a Mirabito Value Plan (MVP).
It’s OUR way of thanking YOU, our valuable customers.  info_outlineAsk for your card to be linked to your home heating account to earn Rewards on home heat purchases or earn cents off at the pump. Earn more Rewards by shopping at Mirabito Convenience Stores and heating your home with Mirabito Energy Products!Store Promotions
Rewards Plus FAQ
  How do I access my account online?
What should I do if I lost my card but don’t want to lose my cents off?
When do my points expire?
Why should I upgrade from my black Rewards Plus card?
How do I access my account online?To access your online Mirabito Rewards Plus account, you must first have a Mirabito Rewards Plus card.  Once you have a card, click on “My Account” in the red bar at the top of this page. On the My Account page, click on “Click Here” under the Rewards Plus Portal. You can also call the Rewards Plus Toll-Free number at 1-866-647-2248 if you need assistance or have forgotten your username/password.  What should I do if I lost my card but don’t want to lose my cents off?In the event you lose your card, you will need to get a new card by any of the following: visit your nearest Mirabito Convenience Store, fill out the online form or call 1-866-647-2248. With the new card present, call 1-866-647-2248 and tell them you would like to add another card to your account. If your previous card is registered, we can add your new card to the old one, and any Rewards you had will remain.  When do my points expire?Cents off redeemed with Mirabito Convenience Stores will expire in 90 days. Cents off redeemed with Mirabito Energy Products will expire in 120 days. This policy can be found in the Terms and Conditions of the Rewards Plus program.  Why should I upgrade from my black Rewards Plus card?The old black Rewards Plus card lacks new features that are now available with the green Rewards Plus card and both Rewards Plus & Payment cards.  Upgrading will allow you to use the green or red card at the pump to earn cents off on purchases. Customers will also receive first time use discounts. To upgrade, call 1-866-647-2248 or visit the nearest Mirabito Convenience Store location.
  If I prepay for my fuel from Mirabito Energy Products, how come the Rewards do not show up right away?
If I had a delivery from Mirabito Energy Products, when do my Rewards show up on my Rewards Plus account?
If I prepay for my fuel from Mirabito Energy Products, how come the Rewards do not show up right away?When you have your Mirabito Home Heat account linked to your Rewards Plus card, you are able to earn Rewards. We do not give Rewards when the purchase is made, Rewards are given as deliveries are made. If you pre-purchased 600 gallons of fuel oil at once, your Rewards would be added in according to when the actual deliveries are made.  If I had a delivery from Mirabito Energy Products, when do my Rewards show up on my Rewards Plus account?Rewards for deliveries in any given month will be added to the account by the third week of the following month. For example, if the delivery was made on November 5th or November 30th, the Rewards should be on the account the third week of December.  
