*Please note: relocation may be required.  Convenience Store ManagerResponsible for day-to-day store operations including and not limited to scheduling, training and supervising employees. Also responsible for store profitability, budget, expense control, inventory levels, shortage control, customer service and safety.
Requirements (including but not limited to): enthusiastic attitude for customer service, flexibility to accommodate sudden schedule changes and ability to be on call 24 hours a day if an emergency arises, exceptional communication skills, ability to motivate employees to achieve the best buying experience possible, ability to achieve performance standards with respect to: store computer, POS machines, cash registers, equipment and particular systems in operations at the location, meet physical demands such as walking, lifting, handling merchandise, etc., possess a high school diploma and experience in retail management.
Currently recruiting for: Syracuse, Ithaca, Binghamton & Oneonta  Convenience Store Sales AssociatesEvery full-time or part-time Sales Associate is responsible for the proper and efficient operation of his or her shift, within company policy, in such a manner as to ensure that the shift contributes to the increased profitability of the location. Provide all customers with the best buying experience through superior customer service.
Requirements include: possess a high school diploma, be able to perform arithmetical calculations in order to be able to make change, complete shift reports, and account for numbers of a variety of products during vendor check-in, be able to stand for long periods of time, meet physical demands such as climbing a ladder, stocking shelves, carrying cases of milk cartons, soft drinks, etc., be able to read and understand instructions for operating electronic cash registers and other equipment, be able to maintain a clean environment, inside and outside of the store, abide by all safety related procedures as required by the company.  View Our Team






















    William Mirabito | Mirabito Energy Products | ZoomInfo.com


