Mr. William Mirabito Named Mirabito VP – Customer Development

May 22, 2014Brent Strignano 




(Binghamton, NY) Mr. Joseph Mirabito, Chief Executive Officer for the Mirabito Family of Companies, has announced that Mr. William Mirabito has been named as Vice President of Customer Development.
Formerly President of Mang Insurance, Mr. Mirabito provides over thirty years of knowledge and expertise in customer service. He will be responsible for improving the development of customer experience and growth.
Mr. Mirabito currently lives in Oneonta with his wife Karen, and has two children.
The Mirabito Family of Companies operates in eight states with multiple divisions including, Natural Gas and Electric, Home Energy Products and Services, Wholesale Energy Products and Services, Convenience Stores, and Mirabito Truck Repair. Mirabito corporate offices are located in The MetroCenter, Binghamton, NY. For more information, visit www.mirabito.com.  


 





